The paper also discusses practical applications, such as online and approximate algorithms, which could place it in the Robotics (cs.RO) or Systems and Control (cs.SY) categories. Finally, the paper involves analysis and formulation of algorithms, which could place it in the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) category.
